text: Karen Marie Aagaard Ørsted Andersen (born in Odense, Denmark in August 13, 1988), better known as Mø, is a Danish singer and pianist. She released her first single "Maiden" in 2012. On March 10, 2014, her first album No Mythologies to Follow was released. ==References== Category:1988 births Category:Living people Category:Danish singers Category:Odense Category:Pianists Category:Synth-pop singers Category:Electropop singers
